claim.claim-text:
5. The image data file management system according to claim 1, wherein said image server further includes a data base section and a backup section; 
said backup section collectively stores a predetermined number of sets of said image data for backup; and 
said data base section stores a position at which said image data is stored and stores an identifier of said backup section used for storing said image data for backup.

7. An image data file management method comprising: 
an image acquisition step of acquiring image data of a subject; 
an information acquisition step of acquiring defect information for judgment upon whether said subject is acceptable with respect to said image data acquired by said image acquisition step; 
a file creation step of performing reversible compression with respect to said image data acquired by said image acquisition step based on judgment information indicating that said subject is rejectable acquired by said information acquisition step and performing nonreversible compression with respect to the same based on judgment information indicating that said subject is acceptable, thereby creating each image data file; and 
an image data recording step of recording said image data file created by said file creation step.
